1352 enum SessionStatus
1353 {
1354  STATUS_AUTHED = 0, // Player authenticated (_player==nullptr, m_playerRecentlyLogout = false or will be reset before handler call)
1355  STATUS_LOGGEDIN, // Player in game (_player!=nullptr, inWorld())
1356  STATUS_TRANSFER, // Player transferring to another map (_player!=nullptr, !inWorld())
1357  STATUS_LOGGEDIN_OR_RECENTLY_LOGGEDOUT, // _player!= nullptr or _player==nullptr && m_playerRecentlyLogout)
1358  STATUS_NEVER, // Opcode not accepted from client (deprecated or server side only)
1359  STATUS_UNHANDLED // We don' handle this opcode yet
1360 };
1361 
1362 enum PacketProcessing
1363 {
1364  PROCESS_INPLACE = 0, // process packet whenever we receive it - mostly for non-handled or non-implemented packets
1365  PROCESS_THREADUNSAFE, // packet is not thread-safe - process it in World::UpdateSessions()
1366  PROCESS_THREADSAFE, // packet is thread-safe - process it in Map::Update()
1367  PROCESS_MAP_THREAD, // packet is map thread safe
1368  PROCESS_IMMEDIATE, // packet is network thread safe
1369 };
